ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:Title: EOX::Maps
ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:Abstract: EOX::Maps are background and overlay maps made of Open Data and designed and provided by EOX.
ows:ServiceIdentification.ows:AccessConstraints: Proper attribution is required for any usage. The attribution shall follow the example of the demo map at https://maps.eox.at in the lower right corner including the respective links e.g. "Terrain { Data © OpenStreetMap contributers and others, Rendering © EOX }" with links to http://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright, https://maps.eox.at/#data, and https://eox.at. Additional restrictions may apply for individual layers as indicated in the respective abstract.
